00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 8=

4
00:01:10,439 --> 00:01:12,560
If it really wanted to eat me,

5
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,519
would Your Majesty

6
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:16,319
kill me?

7
00:01:16,900 --> 00:01:22,300
♪Moon sets on palace walls,
breeze hits the gates♪

8
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:26,560
Yes.

9
00:01:30,540 --> 00:01:36,500
♪Dim lamps, concerns unheard by anyone♪

10
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:38,319
If there comes a day

11
00:01:38,799 --> 00:01:40,480
when Your Majesty wants my life,

12
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,840
I will offer it to you myself.

13
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:50,040
Your Majesty, follow me.

14
00:01:50,190 --> 00:01:51,359
I have something to show you.

15
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,359
I was reading
some ancient records last night

16
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:57,420
and found the insect
the little white snake likes to eat.

17
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:58,630
It's called the Crimson Butterfly.

18
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,879
It's unique on Mount Tian.

19
00:02:00,239 --> 00:02:02,640
There is only one insect
in the capital similar to it.

20
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,159
Hm.

21
00:02:07,439 --> 00:02:08,599
Your Majesty, don't open it.

22
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:11,140
♪I walk through the palace
day and night, just for my beloved♪

23
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:14,900
♪All my tenderness is for you,
I'd stay alone for you♪

24
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:18,540
♪I don't ask for equality,
only that you hear me♪

25
00:02:18,540 --> 00:02:21,780
♪Years of longing haunt
the palace gates, too deep to hide♪

26
00:02:22,300 --> 00:02:23,719
Your Majesty, don't open your eyes.

27
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,520
The fuzz on its wings is poisonous.

28
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,000
Handan,

29
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,919
bring a basin of fresh water.

30
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:31,439
Shen Zhinian, did you do this on purpose?

31
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:32,860
Your Majesty, don't open your mouth.

32
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:34,610
Be careful,
or your mouth will swell up too.

33
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,919
Young Lady, the water is here.

34
00:02:35,919 --> 00:02:36,319
Alright.

35
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:37,800
Wait a moment.

36
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,630
Let me wash it with fresh water for you.

37
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,479
Your Majesty, here.

38
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,560
Your Majesty,

39
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,560
do you feel any better?

40
00:02:59,039 --> 00:03:00,439
If you had such a "good thing",

41
00:03:00,500 --> 00:03:01,890
how could you not share it with me?

42
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:02,960
No,

43
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:03,960
Your Majesty.

44
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,120
Your Majesty, stop it.

45
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:08,919
Young Lady,

46
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,319
Lady Liu of Gentleness is here.

47
00:03:10,919 --> 00:03:11,639
Your Majesty,

48
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:13,879
hide yourself first.

49
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:15,479
You dare to tell me to hide?

50
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:17,280
Is there a guest in your room, Zhinian?

51
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,240
No, there isn't.

52
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,360
I'll be right out.

53
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,000
Hide in here for a moment.

54
00:03:26,110 --> 00:03:27,639
You dare to make me get into a cabinet?

55
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:28,919
No.

56
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,800
I'm afraid if she
knows Your Majesty is here,

57
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,840
she will refuse to leave.

58
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,759
So you think I am
someone who can't be seen?

59
00:03:33,759 --> 00:03:34,960
I didn't mean it like that.

60
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,780
Let me just
send her away first, alright?

61
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:38,240
Hide for a moment.

62
00:03:38,439 --> 00:03:39,759
You'd better think that way.

63
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,390
Ruyan, why do you have
time to visit my Tinglan Palace today?

64
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:51,439
I've come to congratulate you.

65
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,400
Ruyan, please come in.

66
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,360
Please have a seat.

67
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:58,039
I wonder what there is to congratulate?

68
00:03:58,210 --> 00:04:00,520
Your elder sister has been
titled County Princess Ning'an.

69
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:02,639
She's become the favorite
of the Dowager Consort.

70
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:04,520
Is that not a joyous event?

71
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:08,960
Although I am from the Liu family,

72
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,520
you saw how Lady Liu
of Bright Deportment

73
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,319
treated me.

74
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:15,599
Please help me say a few kind words
before the Dowager Consort.

75
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,560
You overestimated me.

76
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,360
In front of the Dowager Consort,

77
00:04:19,380 --> 00:04:20,520
what influence could I have?

78
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:22,160
You have County Princess Ning'an.

79
00:04:28,879 --> 00:04:29,759
Zhinian,

80
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:31,040
please just help me.

81
00:04:37,730 --> 00:04:38,680
Is someone in the room?

82
00:04:38,879 --> 00:04:39,600
No.

83
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:41,240
It might be the cat I'm raising.

84
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,519
We shouldn't let it break your things.

85
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,100
It's better to be careful.

86
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:45,720
Ruyan.

87
00:04:53,700 --> 00:04:54,959
What are you looking for, Ruyan?

88
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,120
Your clothes are too plain.

89
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,920
I'll send a few outfits over another day.

90
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:07,079
You should dress up properly.

91
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:09,240
Don't embarrass County Princess Ning'an.

92
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:11,319
Ruyan, I'm afraid you've misunderstood.

93
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,720
My elder sister

94
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,160
has always looked down on me.

95
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:16,120
Regarding your request,

96
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:18,000
I'm afraid I cannot help.

97
00:05:19,079 --> 00:05:19,959
Never mind.

98
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:22,639
By the way, the Empress Dowager's
birthday is approaching.

99
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,360
I want to choreograph a dance

100
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:25,480
and invite you to join me.

101
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,480
If we team up,

102
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:30,399
we will shine.

103
00:05:31,639 --> 00:05:33,279
Ruyan, I'm afraid
you'll be disappointed.

104
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,560
I am not good at dancing.

105
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,240
I really wish to befriend you, Zhinian.

106
00:05:41,959 --> 00:05:43,319
If you look down on me,

107
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:44,720
I won't bother you anymore.

108
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:56,199
(So he escaped through the window.)

109
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:00,240
Shen Zhinian must be
trying to harm Your Majesty.

110
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,160
She is not.

111
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,680
She didn't.

112
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,399
Your Majesty's eyes are in this state,

113
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,839
yet you still speak for her.

114
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:09,519
Could it be

115
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,399
that you have fallen for her?

116
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,839
How dare you.

117
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,639
I have not fallen for her.

118
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:17,300
My apologies, Your Majesty.

119
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,639
But then again,

120
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,920
her catching insects

121
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,839
was indeed to please me.

122
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,240
Yes,

123
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:27,040
she did it to please Your Majesty.

124
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:30,360
Then, will Your Majesty still
title her Lady of Beauty?

125
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:32,360
I am in no rush, so why are you?

126
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:33,319
Get out.

127
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,079
If there comes a day

128
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:45,480
when Your Majesty wants my life,

129
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,480
I will offer it to you myself.

130
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,160
Little liar.

131
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:02,439
If it wanted to eat me,

132
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,480
would Your Majesty

133
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:06,240
kill me?

134
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:09,600
I would.

135
00:07:10,690 --> 00:07:12,319
(I have been in the palace for so long,)

136
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:15,000
(yet I still haven't gained
Nangong Xuanyu's trust.)

137
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:18,360
(Shen Nanqiao entered
the palace just like in her past life.)

138
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,639
(Lu Jianglin has also gained
the Dowager Consort's favor.)

139
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,399
(Is it possible that everything)

140
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,360
(from my past life will happen again?)

141
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,480
(What should I do?)

142
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:39,199
- Longevity to the Dowager Consort.
- Longevity to the Dowager Consort.

143
00:07:39,199 --> 00:07:40,480
- May your virtue shine forever.
- May your virtue shine forever.

144
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:52,360
Senior Attendant, you're finally back.

145
00:07:53,839 --> 00:07:54,839
What did she call you?

146
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,680
My surname is Chang.

147
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,199
They call me Eunuch Chang.

148
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:10,920
Jianglin and Nanqiao brought back

149
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,990
a thousand-year-old
immortal tree from Nanhua Temple

150
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:14,920
to celebrate my birthday.

151
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:24,800
(Weeping flowering peach blossoms.)

152
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:27,000
(There is an immortal tree in Nanhua,)

153
00:08:27,020 --> 00:08:28,879
(its weeping branches
bearing peach blossoms.)

154
00:08:29,079 --> 00:08:31,040
(But once it leaves Mount Nanhua,)

155
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,360
(it can hardly survive.)

156
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,919
This tree is called
the Weeping Peach Tree.

157
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,720
It is a thousand years old.

158
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:39,720
Not only is it vibrant and beautiful,

159
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:42,000
but its fruit can also
strengthen the body

160
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,120
and prolong one's life.

161
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:45,399
Transplanting this tree was difficult.

162
00:08:45,399 --> 00:08:47,960
Fortunately,
Young Master Lu is widely learned,

163
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:50,679
and Nanqiao is an expert in flora.

164
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:53,480
Only then could it be
brought to the capital safely.

165
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:55,840
Lu Jianglin, you've earned
the Dowager Consort's favor.

166
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,360
That was not an easy task.

167
00:08:59,679 --> 00:09:00,879
I have little talent,

168
00:09:01,300 --> 00:09:03,720
but I am willing to serve
Your Majesty like a dog or a horse.

169
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,320
I don't lack dogs or horses.

170
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,799
Besides, if I were to ride you
like a horse,

171
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,970
I'm afraid the Dowager Consort
wouldn't be pleased.

172
00:09:21,399 --> 00:09:22,120
Your Majesty,

173
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:23,200
Dowager Consort,

174
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:25,919
I would like to perform
a peach blossom dance.

175
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,320
Ruyan, you're a gifted dancer.

176
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:29,000
Go ahead and perform a piece.

177
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,759
What does Your Majesty think?

178
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:31,720
Alright.

179
00:09:33,090 --> 00:09:34,840
Senior Attendant Rou
is also a good dancer.

180
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:37,759
I would like to invite her

181
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:39,639
to dance with me.

182
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,039
I am clumsy.

183
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:48,990
I fear I might ruin your mood,
Dowager Consort.

184
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,519
Zhinian once suffered a leg injury.

185
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:55,759
She really cannot dance.

186
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,200
Zhinian?

187
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:58,960
Young Master Lu, you call her

188
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,519
a bit too intimately, don't you?

189
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,879
Young Master Lu came from a poor family.

190
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,830
He once studied
at the Shen family's academy.

191
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,399
He was my father's personal student.

192
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:08,879
Nanqiao, Young Master Lu, and I

193
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:10,520
have known each other since childhood.

194
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,879
Lu watched her grow up.

195
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,759
He is like an older brother to her.

196
00:10:16,159 --> 00:10:17,320
In that case,

197
00:10:17,559 --> 00:10:19,080
there is no need to be formal.

198
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,840
Join Ruyan

199
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,080
and dance a piece together.

200
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,960
Yes.

201
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:56,240
(There is the scent
of Love Potion on her silk.)

202
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:06,039
(So, she plans to frame Lu Jianglin.)

203
00:11:06,220 --> 00:11:07,559
(Once Lu Jianglin loses control)

204
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:08,639
(and comes after me...)

205
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:16,919
The second dance,

206
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,960
The Drunken Concubine.

207
00:11:33,639 --> 00:11:35,440
(This is the drugged cup.)

208
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:38,799
What is it?

209
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,679
Why did she fall?

210
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,159
What happened?

211
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,559
What a "Mouse Playing
Under the Moon" dance.

212
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,120
I am impressed.

213
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,440
So hot...

214
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,159
It's so hot.

215
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,039
Lady Liu,

216
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,000
what are you doing?

217
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:07,240
You slut.

218
00:12:07,759 --> 00:12:08,799
You slut.

219
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:10,919
How disrespectful.

220
00:12:11,279 --> 00:12:12,600
Drag her out now.

221
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:18,240
How can such improper behavior
be acceptable before the throne?

222
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,399
The peach tree...

223
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,559
How could this be?

224
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,240
Look, what's going on?

225
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,879
This is an ill omen.

226
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,759
On the peach tree...

227
00:12:30,879 --> 00:12:31,679
Look.

228
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,240
Senior Attendant Rou,

229
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:37,639
just what have you done?

230
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,320
This is the immortal tree

231
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,990
I prepared for
the Dowager Consort's birthday.

232
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:41,799
Presumptuous!

233
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:43,600
How dare you curse me?

234
00:12:43,759 --> 00:12:44,519
Guards,

235
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:47,039
send Shen Zhinian to the Cold Palace.

236
00:12:57,880 --> 00:13:03,000
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

237
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:09,960
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

238
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,960
♪If we don't meet♪

239
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:17,400
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

240
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:24,120
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

241
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:30,920
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

242
00:13:31,280 --> 00:13:37,600
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

243
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:44,800
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

244
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:51,680
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

245
00:13:51,920 --> 00:13:57,800
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

246
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:05,320
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

247
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:12,160
♪Wanting to fold
my heart into a paper kite♪

248
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:18,880
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

